    "Indiscriminate sensor fusion may not lead to an optimal odometry solution.",
    "Hence, thorough planning and a precise grasp of each sensor's specific requirements are crucial prerequisites before deploying sensor fusion.The classifications of LiDAR odometry introduced so far can be organized into a unified pipeline, as shown in Fig. 3.",
    "The figure illustrates how additional sensors can be incorporated into a LiDAR odometry system, guiding the determination of sensor usage and data integration strategies.",
    "Remaining challengesUndeniably, LiDAR odometry technologies have witnessed significant advancements in providing high-quality positions for mobile robots and autonomous vehicles, with their performance demonstrated in various real-world environments [36,165].",
    "However, despite these significant advancements, unresolved issues remain valuable for further research."
